{"tid":793570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老母交帶落如果佢中風唔好打999，點反駁佢","createTime":"2018-08-25T13:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T15:12:05.000Z","uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"48bdb92fdd3b500de5b1df215d1a346533bfa85f","tid":793570,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"佢話驚到時送左去廣華<br />\n佢話要叫St John. 唔好叫999<br />\n睇完下面段野就信到100%<br />\n我心諗上到救護車，個司機會聽你講就奇啦<br />\n人地都有protocol要跟<br />\n邊有得指定醫院架<br />\n<br />\n=================================<br />\n<br />\n上星期五有客戶深夜在家中懷疑中風，馬上報警，救傷車來後表示會送到廣華醫院，朋友知道九龍伊利沙伯醫院才有 24小時 中風治療，要求救護員一定要去伊利沙伯急症室。<br />\n到院即時照 CT Scan，照完後打溶血針，半小時後，看她已經行動自如，回復正常，真是很神奇。<br />\n<br />\n其實當照 CT Scan 時，即時同步傳輸資料到腦神經專科医生，經他診断後决定即時打溶血針，溶血針要在 3小時 內注射才有效，謹記！謹記！<br />\n<br />\n現時全港有 24小時 中風打溶血針服務的政府醫院有<br />\n1）伊利沙伯醫院 ✔<br />\n2）威爾斯醫院 ✔<br />\n3）瑪麗醫院 ✔<br />\n4）東區尤德醫院 ✔<br />\n而私家醫院只有 仁安醫院 ✔<br />\n<br />\n一定要記住那一間是在附近的醫院，救命的，不要去錯！<br />\n如果 call 999 叫救護車，係唔可以要求送誇區醫院！<br />\n但 call ☎ 1878000，聖約翰救護車就可以。<br />\n/01 2018"},{"pid":"41490f0a21e1b9ddfe5cc28c8929e606c4a695f3","tid":793570,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"聽佢第一句好了"},{"pid":"04a3be3f9bbc04727ed0ddca65308ee24aef9a3a","tid":793570,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"打佢老母個仔"},{"pid":"812a80c0625d08c0ce182537b9fc0bc70ad32372","tid":793570,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"咁咪打112囉"},{"pid":"0253ac4b5810045b9ac96aa125d93e572b3f23a7","tid":793570,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"佢中左風阻止到你先算啦<br />\n唔洗反駁佢<br />\n到時照打999"},{"pid":"259ceb163b765bbca8cc2a44797a905bd32afc9d","tid":793570,"uid":72759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1985120/%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%20%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E9%87%9D%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%95%B1%E6%89%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1985120%2F%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A2%25A8%2520%25E6%25BA%25B6%25E8%25A1%2580%25E9%2587%259D%25E9%259D%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2595%25B1%25E6%2589%2593&d=bAnuM%2BJEB%2BOsMDlKFD%2FnsgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7668625a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1985120/%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%20%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E9%87%9D%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%95%B1%E6%89%93</a>"},{"pid":"382d70c4d453f0837010bb3152a36f556cee695b","tid":793570,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259ceb163b765bbca8cc2a44797a905bd32afc9d","tid":793570,"uid":72759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1985120/%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%20%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E9%87%9D%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%95%B1%E6%89%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1985120%2F%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2595%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A2%25A8%2520%25E6%25BA%25B6%25E8%25A1%2580%25E9%2587%259D%25E9%259D%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2595%25B1%25E6%2589%2593&d=bAnuM%2BJEB%2BOsMDlKFD%2FnsgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7668625a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1985120/%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%20%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E9%87%9D%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%95%B1%E6%89%93</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"其實樓主老母冇講錯晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為要受溶血治療嘅話一定要短時間內發現之後照ct又盛再班隊team出來做野<br />\n務求如果合適既話推到入黎要1個鐘內可以打針<br />\n做完又要closely monitored好大機會去icu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且中風後過左4.5小時基本上又唔打得<br />\n所以無acute stroke unit當值嘅話根本無可能做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有屋企人疑似中風又唔係辦公時間推去有acute stroke unit嘅醫院的確係一個更加好既選擇(當然而家唔淨止樓主post果幾間啦)"}]}